    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy her! This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014seriously, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garage-kept and spotless. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. You won't find another one this clean! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
