    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3, a pinnacle of atmospheric engineering. This specimen features the S54B32 inline-six, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and high-pressure dual-VANOS system, both of which have been meticulously serviced to ensure optimal cam timing and throttle response. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential, providing visceral mechanical feedback. Critically, the rear subframe mounting points have been reinforced to prevent floor pan fatigue, and the rod bearings have been replaced as a preventative measure. The suspension retains its original kinematics with fresh OEM bushings and dampers, ensuring the chassis remains taut and communicative. The exterior maintains its factory luster with zero signs of panel gap deviation or paint thickness inconsistency. This is a mechanically transparent, turnkey vehicle for the serious collector.",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
