    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-grade vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous preservation. This car is in absolute pristine condition, featuring a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like luster and not a single stone chip or swirl mark. The interior is equally immaculate, boasting supple, hand-stitched leather that remains firm and 'as-new,' free from any wear or creasing. Every electronic component and driver-assist feature functions perfectly, just as it did the day it left the factory. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach; it has been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships, with a comprehensive folder of maintenance records included. Always garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and never driven in inclement weather, this vehicle represents a rare opportunity for a discerning collector to acquire a masterpiece of automotive engineering in its finest possible state.",
      "price": 48500.0,
