    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total stunner! This car is in truly pristine condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it tucked away in a garage and maintaining it meticulously. It drives like an absolute dream! I know I'm still building my rating here, so I\u2019d love for you to come check it out in person and see for yourself just how flawless it really is. Let\u2019s get you behind the wheel of your dream car!",
