    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in concours-ready condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, exhibiting perfect compression across all cylinders and a meticulously maintained VANOS system. The induction note from the individual throttle bodies is crisp, paired with a Getrag 6-speed manual that offers tactile, notch-free engagement. Mechanically, the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced, and the chassis retains its factory-spec torsional rigidity with zero bushing deflection. The exterior retains its original deep luster with no paint metered outside factory tolerances, while the interior\u2019s Nappa leather remains supple and free of bolster wear. This is a turn-key collector piece for the discerning enthusiast seeking peak M-division engineering.",
